title: Large 1BD Sunny Apartment w/ outdoor deck!
posting_body: ft. apartment is light & bright and features a spacious deck for your private barbecues, alfresco dining, & sunsets.
The open concept kitchen and living space feature granite counter tops, a raised bar top, large windows, new carpet, and fresh painted walls.
The bedroom includes a closet and separate laundry room with washer/dryer and organizer.
The full bathroom has plenty of cabinet space & a tub shower.
Reserved, secure parking garage stalls available $125/month.
Ravenna offers fantastic locally owned shops, bakeries, & restaurants including the 2018 James Beard Award wining “Best New Restaurant in America” Junebaby.
Third Place Books, community center, fitness/Pilates/yoga studios, fruit & vegetable stand, community pea-patch, & quiet parks are all a short walk from your door.
On bus lines 71 & 72 with easy access to I-5 & 520 Bridge.
